.caution.message Add <code>[novalidate]</code> to the form to bypass browser-native validation
  | and use this library instead.

h2 Email address
.message <code>[data-match-id]</code> needs to match an <code>input[id]</code> for confirmation fields.
form(novalidate)
  .row
    .col-6
      label A required email address
        .required Required
        input#email(type="email" required)
        .error Enter a valid email address
    .col-6
      label Confirm email address
        .required Required
        input(type="email" data-match-id="email")
        .error Email addresses don’t match
  .row
    .col-12
      button(type="submit") Test email addresses

hr
h2 Select
.message Required selections should just default to the first option.
form(novalidate)
  .row
    .col-6
      label A required selection
        .required Required
        select
          option foo
          option bar
          option baz
    .col-6
      label An optional selection
        select
          option(disabled selected) Select somthing if you want…
          option foo
          option bar
          option baz

